<item>
            <title>[LU-7359] Interop 2.5.5&lt;-&gt;master: conf-sanity test_90b: MDT start failed</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7359</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Saurabh Tandan &amp;lt;saurabh.tandan@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/3d20050a-7b68-11e5-a83c-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/3d20050a-7b68-11e5-a83c-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_90b failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;MDT start failed
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue has been only observed in case of full group and when server and client have different versions running on them i.e. in case of interop.&lt;br/&gt;
test log:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== conf-sanity test 90b: check max_mod_rpcs_in_flight is enforced after update == 22:57:55 (1445727475)
start mds service on shadow-25vm8
CMD: shadow-25vm8 mkdir -p /mnt/mds1
CMD: shadow-25vm8 test -b /dev/lvm-Role_MDS/P1
Starting mds1:   /dev/lvm-Role_MDS/P1 /mnt/mds1
CMD: shadow-25vm8 mkdir -p /mnt/mds1; mount -t lustre   		                   /dev/lvm-Role_MDS/P1 /mnt/mds1
shadow-25vm8: mount.lustre: according to /etc/mtab /dev/mapper/lvm--Role_MDS-P1 is already mounted on /mnt/mds1
Start of /dev/lvm-Role_MDS/P1 on mds1 failed 17
 conf-sanity test_90b: @@@@@@ FAIL: MDT start failed 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It is related to &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7082&quot; title=&quot;conf-sanity test_90b: MDT start failed&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-7082&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-7082&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Server: 2.5.5&lt;br/&gt;
Client: master, build# 3225, RHEL 6.7</environment>
